{"tid":764063,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後真係扮文青扮上腦？搭地鐵睇乜能野書？仲要睇英文書扮哂野！","createTime":"2018-08-01T15:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T13:27:47.000Z","uid":19334,"like":37,"dislike":232,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"018db5b14b8f3a96467bf79335079e455ac26acf","tid":764063,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩放工搭地鐵，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同隻90後一齊收工，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁一齊坐底諗住同佢吹下水啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢係佢個文青書包到拎左本書出黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問我有無睇過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我連書名都唔識讀，咁就無理佢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者就佢坐左係我隔離睇書，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路上車睇到落車，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔係唔知人多，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拎住本書扮博士搏比人鬧咩？<br />\n<br />\n扮文青就唔該死遠少少，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好阻住人地嘛 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最心涼就係落車果陣有個地盤佬唔小心一野拍左佢本書落地，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係咁有學識就唔洗搭交通公具先黎睇書扮文青啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef519cd0538d29f2de5b4d15f70347ad64d189e1","tid":764063,"uid":34103,"like":6,"dislike":49,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcc63d40def86505cb907be6e35827678ec2a40f","tid":764063,"uid":398,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"講得好，有道理！"},{"pid":"a18d3e13620342340d3